title: Dayane da Rocha
text:
Dayane de Fátima da Rocha is a Brazilian <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="Striker%20%28association%20football%29">striker</a>, currently playing for <a href="Ternana%20Futsal">Ternana Futsal</a> in <a href="Italy">Italy</a>'s <a href="Serie%20A%20%28women%27s%20football%29">Serie A</a>. She previously played for <a href="Club%20Irex%20Puebla">Irex Puebla</a> and <a href="Sporting%20Huelva">Sporting Huelva</a> in <a href="Spain">Spain</a>'s <a href="Primera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20%28women%29">Superliga</a>.
She was a member of the <a href="Brazil%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Brazilian national team</a> in the <a href="Football%20at%20the%202004%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20tournament">2004 Summer Olympics</a>.
